Invocation Name: dependency lookup
des:
This skill tells you in which dependency a class is located in the Android SDKs. Simply say "Alexa, ask Dependency Lookup where do I find wallet" to find out which dependency you need to include.

New: Now also in English
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
